freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: After receipt of 2nd vaccine, where I broke a bone in my foot which recently healed, I began to feel a dull pain which had been gone. Also a bit of depression.
Apathy-depression feelings much better. More energy too
Have been very thirsty and drinking more water.

I have the Covid 19 pink eye symptom since 2-19-21 in the late afternoon. It hurts a lot. Burning and pain and redness and watery eyes. Just my right eye. I am immune compromised diagnosed with CVID. Feel free to contact me. I have never had this eye symptom in my life.
Just to let you know I have Common Variable Immune Deficiency and get monthly IGG infusions. It will be interesting to find out how much immunity I will get from the vaccine.

Last nite I had a headache. At 2am I woke from sleeping with severe pain across my shoulders and chest area across clavicle. It felt like pain and deep pressure I had never felt before. At 10:15 am I got a rapid Covid test which came out negative. I still have some pain in and around clavicle chest area but not as severe as last night.

Nightmares and somewhat lethargic/depressed and tired. Better than yesterday though. My almost healed broken foot more painful since vaccine and interestingly my left arm location of 1st vaccine became painful again yesterday like my right arm 2nd vaccine location
Realky tired and exhausted. Slept a long time
The pain in my broken foot that was gone just prior to the 2nd vaccine returned. Still hurts .
